Pupil
=====

1. Run Pupil Capture
--------------------

$ sudo ./run-pupil.sh
<enter password>
We are then inside the Docker container. Launch the application:
# python pupil_src/capture/main.py

Enable Pupil Server and Pupil Remote plugins.
FIXME: enable those plugins automatically.

2. Run cosy-pupil-server
------------------------

In a new terminal:

$ sudo ./run-cosy-pupil-server.sh
<enter password>
Inside the container:
# ./external-recorder

3. Calibration
--------------

Do the calibration with Pupil Capture.

4. Run cosy-pupil-client
------------------------

From Matlab, run the experiment.
